    "Our comprehensive discussion on the value derived from blockchain projects underscores their significance while re-evaluating key risks, including a personal reflection from the author on the potential risks.",
    "The question that emerges from this review paper is, if we fast forward ten years, would all the transactions that we perform in our society be in fiat currencies, and the answer is that most probably they won't.",
    "With the emergence of Web3, assets, money and marketplaces will become interconnected, and some of the cryptocurrencies will form part of these new digital assets, but would that be Bitcoin, or some of the other 22,250 cryptos that are in circulation today, that is difficult to predict.",
